        "text": "<p data-aid=\"141536826\" id=\"note19_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.14?lang=eng#p14\">1&#xA0;Peter 4:14<\/a>. Remember also the promises cited in <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.18?lang=eng#p18\">2&#xA0;Nephi 9:18<\/a> and <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/12.12?lang=eng#p12\">3&#xA0;Nephi 12:12<\/a>.<\/p>",
