        "pid": "141535620",
        "id": "note17",
        "text": "<p data-aid=\"141536820\" id=\"note17_p1\">Jo Anne Rushton, in Hawes, &#x201C;<a class=\"cross-ref\" href=\"/study/ensign/1994/04/its-good-to-be-alive?lang=eng\">It&#x2019;s Good to Be Alive<\/a>,&#x201D; 43.<\/p>",
